        <h3>Tips for getting page ranges right</h3>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Open the PDF first</strong> and scroll to confirm which pages you need. Page numbers in the document's footer may not match the actual PDF page number (if there's a cover page or Roman numeral pages)</li>
