        </p>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Pros:</strong> No tool needed, works immediately, built into Chrome</li>
          <li><strong>Cons:</strong> Re-renders the PDF (may change formatting slightly), no batch splitting, can't extract non-continuous pages easily</li>
